{"id":301287,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/维权网-湖南维权人士尹卫和被关11天黑监狱后获释/","date":"2013-06-28T20:32:29Z","modified":"2013-06-28T20:32:29Z","title":"维权网 | 湖南维权人士尹卫和被关11天黑监狱后获释","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员刀峰报道）本网获悉：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>点半</span><span>，湖南省湘乡市维权人士尹卫和被当地警方从家中带走，关押在湘乡市国土局对面的水月洞天商务宾馆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8206</span><span>和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8208</span><span>两套房内。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>点左右，尹卫和被当地公安局局长、政法委书记、乡政府党委书记等人释放，回到家中。尹卫和这次被关监狱，是当地公安人员以法制学习班为由使他失去自由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>尹卫和，男，汉族，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1971</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日</span><span>出生，家住湖南省湘乡市育段乡东塘铺村王家屋塘组</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span><span>号。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年因发起要求政治改革，推进法制建设的签名，而被指控要炸掉毛泽东的故居，以“爆炸罪、破坏电力设施实施罪”判刑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>个月。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>这次之所被当局关黑监狱，据尹卫和说，是因为他宣传反对腐败，要求官员财产公开，向当局呼吁立即释放丁家喜、王永红、李蔚、赵常春等人，并申请游行示威；还了解了中国毒大米的来源，由湿稻谷打甘草灵后，就直接送粮站或米厂，并将事实公布；加上六四到了，当局为了维稳所采取的措施。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>尹卫和电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18907322349</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-69W23MK4a6o/Uc2rGzL3PYI/AAAAAAAAkcg/XBgC7gQtitg/s500/1367314123420.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-69W23MK4a6o/Uc2rGzL3PYI/AAAAAAAAkcg/XBgC7gQtitg/s320/1367314123420.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}